org.apache.ambari.server.orm.dao

Class ExtensionDAO

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ambari.server.orm.dao.ExtensionDAO

  • public class ExtensionDAO
extends Object
    The ExtensionDAO class is used to manage the persistence and retrieval of ExtensionEntity instances. An extension version is like a stack version but it contains custom services. Linking an extension version to the current stack version allows the cluster to install the custom services contained in the extension version.
